          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus is good and nature friendly so feels comfortable.",
          "name": "Karan Anant Bari",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "It provides various different courses and opportunities.",
          "name": "Karan Anant Bari",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are two canteens in our college campus. Food is tasty. We used to spend more time there.",
